Privacy Policy
Effective Date:
28 December 2024
API Testing Tool ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle data collected through our application.
1. Data Collection
Our app does not collect, process, or transmit any personal or sensitive data to external servers. All data is stored locally on your device in a SQLite database.
2. Data Storage
All data created, configured, or saved by you is securely stored locally on your device.
No external servers or third parties have access to this data.
3. Data Usage
The data you provide is solely used to enhance your experience within the app. We do not analyze, share, or monetize the data in any way.
4. Data Security
We implement reasonable measures to protect your data stored in the SQLite database. However, the security of your device is your responsibility. Ensure your device is protected with a passcode or other security measures.
5. User Responsibility
You are responsible for backing up any data stored locally, as it cannot be recovered if the app or device is deleted or damaged.
If you share your device with others, they may access data saved locally.
6. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be reflected in the app, and the updated policy will include the new effective date.
7. Contact Us
If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
support@besolutions.store
.
By using API Testing Tool, you agree to this Privacy Policy. Thank you for trusting API Testing Tool.